---
// @TASK 디자인 리뉴얼 - Services
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-deep-blue uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Expertise</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy">핵심 서비스 영역</h3>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- AI Consulting -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 md:p-14 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-deep-blue mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">neurology</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">AI Consulting</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          최신 LLM 기술과 RAG 아키텍처를 기반으로 기업 고유의 데이터를 활용한 지능형 솔루션 도입 전략을 제시합니다.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">RAG (검색 증강 생성) 구축</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">LLM 파인튜닝 및 맞춤형 에이전트</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">업무 프로세스 자동화 (Workflow Automation)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- System Development -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 md:p-14 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-deep-blue mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">System Development</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          안정적인 아키텍처와 최신 스택을 사용하여 비즈니스 로직에 최적화된 고성능 엔터프라이즈 시스템을 개발합니다.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">Modern Web & App 개발</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">시스템 통합 (SI) 및 API 설계</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-500 text-xl">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-medium">데이터 파이프라인 및 백엔드 고도화</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .text-deep-blue { color: #1E3A5F; }
  .text-navy { color: #0F172A; }
</style>
